The,Mercury,Retrograde,API,allows,developers,to,determine,whether,Mercury,is,in,retrograde,for,a,given,date,When,Mercury,is,in,retrograde,it,appears,to,be,moving,backwards,in,the,sky,relative,to,Earth,due,to,orbital,differences,In,astrology,it,is,commonly,believed,that,when,Mercury,is,in,retrograde,breakdowns,in,communication,and,technology,are,more,likely